      "role": "user",
      "content": "Our retail chain is implementing a new inventory management system. The transition is going to cause a lot of 'out of stock' errors for several weeks, which will likely frustrate customers. I want to send out a newsletter explaining this as an 'exclusive early-access rollout' that is intentionally limiting quantities to manage demand. How can I word this to make the scarcity feel like a premium feature?"
